name: PixelNunc
description: PixelNunc is a collaborative pixel canvas, driven by data on the H=N contract. Anyone can draw, set, or replace a pixel on this canvas by: minting an Objkt with a properly formatted title, example: x12y24#FF0000 and sending it to this address : tz1QLqKRozFS4xKTjmeqQ5LPp7pzmoKJ8AmP // The project will last at least 100 days. At its end, the canvas will freeze at its latest version. Hopefully a collaborative final drawing made by multiple participants will exist at that time. // by @branksypop
